{"tid":2436000,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"參議院通過修改版的1.9萬億刺激方案，將發回眾議院作最後審核","createTime":"2021-03-06T17:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T19:52:52.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"81d1bd1204d54a90f34f161009cb88690688fd94","tid":2436000,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>Senate passes Biden&rsquo;s COVID relief bill, sending legislation with $1,400 stimulus checks to House</strong><br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON &ndash; The Democratic-controlled Senate Saturday overcame Republican roadblocks and a debate that lasted beyond 24 hours to pass President Joe Biden's $1.9 trillion COVID-19 relief package which would provide millions of Americans with $1,400 direct payments, billions of dollars for vaccine distribution, and funds to help reopen schools and colleges.<br />\n<br />\nThe chamber passed the bill following a session that began around 9 a.m. Friday and ended at approximately 12:30 p.m. on Saturday, aft a &quot;vote-a-rama&quot; of proposed changes from both parties. The final vote was 50-49 with all Republicans voting against the measure and all members of the Senate Democratic caucus supporting it. Sen. Dan Sullivan, R-Alaska, was not present for the vote."},{"pid":"885a0d438cb0c5f2ca3aa0622a725733bd2abd85","tid":2436000,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-06/senate-passes-1-9-trillion-relief-package-after-marathon-votes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-03-06%2Fsenate-passes-1-9-trillion-relief-package-after-marathon-votes&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=27fd82c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-06/senate-passes-1-9-trillion-relief-package-after-marathon-votes</a>"},{"pid":"be19db2ce86d0d3541b54849ca59006e